  <brief_title>An Observational Study of CPT-11 Plus Platinum Analogues Regimens and UGT1A1 Genotypes in Solid Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Observational Study of the Efficacy and Safety of CPT-11 Plus Platinum Analogues Regimens for UGT1A1 Genotype Guided Patients With Several Solid Tumors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
