  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the correlation between UGT1A1 genotypes and the
      safety of CPT-11 plus platinum analogues (cisplatin, carboplatin and nedaplatin) regimens for
      patients with lung cancer, cervical cancer, ovarian cancer and gastric cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
